\'93Good afternoon and thank you for the opportunity to present this paper today on FDI networks. My name is John Schoeneman and I am currently a PhD candidate at Penn State. My coauthors, Dr. Zhu and Dr. Desmarais, are both professors at Penn State.\'94\
\
