*** Slide 11/15 ***\
\
"Also, and most important, is that the network terms,  reciprocity and transitivity, are significant and positive , with the bars representing 95% CI, for all years. This supports our hypotheses regarding the network dependencies and demonstrates that models that do not control for these dependencies violate independence assumptions.\'94\
